OL,3,CDisposable vapes to be banned in
OL,4,CGuernsey
OL,6,FSelling, importing and supplying
OL,7,Fdisposable vapes will become a
OL,8,Fcriminal offence in .
OL,10,FIt is after States Members voted
OL,11,Foverwhelmingly to introduce a ban.
OL,13,FThe sale of all vapes to under-18s and
OL,14,Fsmoking in vehicles with children will
OL,15,Falso be outlawed.
OL,17,FDeputy Al Brouard, President of
OL,18,FGuernsey's Health and Social Care
OL,19,FCommittee, says: "I think it's very
OL,20,Fimportant because we just don't know
OL,21,Fthe long-term effects of vaping.
