OL,6,F"It's a very good substitute for
OL,7,Fadults who are trying to give up
OL,8,Fsmoking but we just do not know the
OL,9,Flong-term effects for children, being
OL,10,Faddicted to vapes that contain
OL,11,Fnicotine is also problematic."
OL,13,FUnlike the UK, there are currently no
OL,14,Frestrictions over who can buy vapes in
OL,15,FGuernsey - leaving the decision down
OL,16,Fto the individual sellers.
OL,18,FThe move to tougher laws comes after
OL,19,Freports children as in the Channel
OL,20,FIslands.
